Class Dock

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Thing>

    public class Dock
extends Thing
    The class Dock represents a instance of a Dock. Docks have a SeaPort as a parent and can be the parent of a Ship (i.e., have a ship assigned to it).
